[2026-03-11T00:27:32Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SaaYnQRngw2QrNbf2wCvHR","type":"tool_result","content":"     1Ôćĺworkflow \"develop\" {\n     2Ôćĺ  step implement {\n     3Ôćĺ    prompt = file(\"prompts/implement.md\")\n     4Ôćĺ    results = [success, fail]\n     5Ôćĺ  }\n     6Ôćĺ\n     7Ôćĺ  step test {\n     8Ôćĺ    run = \"bundle exec rake test 2>&1\"\n     9Ôćĺ    results = [success, fail]\n    10Ôćĺ  }\n    11Ôćĺ\n    12Ôćĺ  step lint {\n    13Ôćĺ    run = \"bundle exec rubocop 2>&1\"\n    14Ôćĺ    results = [success, fail]\n    15Ôćĺ  }\n    16Ôćĺ\n    17Ôćĺ  step quality {\n    18Ôćĺ    run = \"python3 scripts/quality-check.py 2>&1\"\n    19Ôćĺ    results = [success, fail]\n    20Ôćĺ  }\n    21Ôćĺ\n    22Ôćĺ  step fix {\n    23Ôćĺ    prompt = file(\"prompts/fix.md\")\n    24Ôćĺ    max_attempts = \"2\"\n    25Ôćĺ    results = [success, fail, give-up]\n    26Ôćĺ  }\n    27Ôćĺ\n    28Ôćĺ  implement:success -> test\n    29Ôćĺ  implement:fail -> abort\n    30Ôćĺ\n    31Ôćĺ  test:success -> lint\n    32Ôćĺ  test:success -> quality\n    33Ôćĺ  test:fail -> fix\n    34Ôćĺ\n    35Ôćĺ  lint:fail -> fix\n    36Ôćĺ  quality:fail -> fix\n    37Ôćĺ  collect all(lint:success, quality:success) -> done\n    38Ôćĺ\n    39Ôćĺ  fix:success -> test\n    40Ôćĺ  fix:fail -> abort\n    41Ôćĺ  fix:give-up -> abort\n    42Ôćĺ}\n    43Ôćĺ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Dpfoc28ynQqDwHgSbSci6o","session_id":"2f8bcbbf-b8aa-4f20-9779-dee3a5fa668b","uuid":"0178c560-7da1-41a6-8fc3-ac494afa254e"}
