[2026-03-11T00:29:45Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DY228HuFrWkftN6vuSs4te","type":"tool_result","content":"     1Ôćĺ# Cloche MVP Implementation Plan\n     2Ôćĺ\n     3Ôćĺ> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.\n     4Ôćĺ\n     5Ôćĺ**Goal:** Build a working Cloche MVP ÔÇö parse workflow DSL, execute steps in Docker containers, report status via gRPC.\n     6Ôćĺ\n     7Ôćĺ**Architecture:** Three Go binaries (cloche, cloched, cloche-agent) with hexagonal architecture. Domain types and DSL parser are the foundation. Build bottom-up: domain -> DSL -> engine -> agent binary -> daemon -> CLI.\n     8Ôćĺ\n     9Ôćĺ**Tech Stack:** Go 1.22+, protobuf/gRPC, Docker SDK, SQLite (via modernc.org/sqlite ÔÇö pure Go), testify for assertions.\n    10Ôćĺ\n    11Ôćĺ---\n    12Ôćĺ\n    13Ôćĺ## Phase 1: Foundation\n    14Ôćĺ\n    15Ôćĺ### Task 1: Initialize Go Module and Directory Structure\n    16Ôćĺ\n    17Ôćĺ**Files:**\n    18Ôćĺ- Create: `go.mod`\n    19Ôćĺ- Create: `Makefile`\n    20Ôćĺ- Create: `cmd/cloche/main.go`\n    21Ôćĺ- Create: `cmd/cloched/main.go`\n    22Ôćĺ- Create: `cmd/cloche-agent/main.go`\n    23Ôćĺ\n    24Ôćĺ**Step 1: Initialize Go module**\n    25Ôćĺ\n    26Ôćĺ```bash\n    27Ôćĺcd /home/lucas/workspace/cloche\n    28Ôćĺgo mod init github.com/cloche-dev/cloche\n    29Ôćĺ```\n    30Ôćĺ\n    31Ôćĺ**Step 2: Create directory structure**\n    32Ôćĺ\n    33Ôćĺ```bash\n    34Ôćĺmkdir -p cmd/cloche cmd/cloched cmd/cloche-agent\n    35Ôćĺmkdir -p internal/domain internal/ports\n    36Ôćĺmkdir -p internal/adapters/docker internal/adapters/sqlite\n    37Ôćĺmkdir -p internal/adapters/grpc internal/adapters/agents/generic\n    38Ôćĺmkdir -p internal/adapters/agents/claudecode\n    39Ôćĺmkdir -p internal/dsl internal/engine internal/protocol\n    40Ôćĺ```\n    41Ôćĺ\n    42Ôćĺ**Step 3: Create placeholder mains**\n    43Ôćĺ\n    44Ôćĺ`cmd/cloche/main.go`:\n    45Ôćĺ```go\n    46Ôćĺpackage main\n    47Ôćĺ\n    48Ôćĺfunc main() {}\n    49Ôćĺ```\n    50Ôćĺ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AzU8HeMxKGnzFPbbezeUQh","session_id":"b83aa53c-b539-403e-957d-d27f065bd09c","uuid":"7c9bf317-7dfb-4b74-8b4f-26c4ecf128f3"}
