[2026-03-11T00:29:45Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01B8wAbK75YxMqkDp7j9xGgM","type":"tool_result","content":"     1Ôćĺ# Design: `cloche init`\n     2Ôćĺ\n     3Ôćĺ## Purpose\n     4Ôćĺ\n     5ÔćĺScaffold a Cloche project in the current directory so a user can go from\n     6Ôćĺzero to `cloche run` with minimal setup.\n     7Ôćĺ\n     8Ôćĺ## CLI Interface\n     9Ôćĺ\n    10Ôćĺ```\n    11Ôćĺcloche init [--workflow <name>] [--image <base-image>]\n    12Ôćĺ```\n    13Ôćĺ\n    14Ôćĺ| Flag | Default | Description |\n    15Ôćĺ|------|---------|-------------|\n    16Ôćĺ| `--workflow` | `develop` | Workflow name; creates `<name>.cloche` |\n    17Ôćĺ| `--image` | `ubuntu:24.04` | Base Docker image for Dockerfile |\n    18Ôćĺ\n    19ÔćĺNo flags required. Bare `cloche init` works with sensible defaults.\n    20Ôćĺ\n    21Ôćĺ## Generated Files\n    22Ôćĺ\n    23Ôćĺ```\n    24Ôćĺ.\n    25ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ <workflow>.cloche\n    26ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ Dockerfile\n    27ÔćĺÔööÔöÇÔöÇ prompts/\n    28Ôćĺ    ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ implement.md\n    29Ôćĺ    ÔööÔöÇÔöÇ fix.md\n    30Ôćĺ```\n    31Ôćĺ\n    32Ôćĺ### Workflow (`develop.cloche`)\n    33Ôćĺ\n    34ÔćĺGeneric 3-step: implement, test, fix loop. Placeholder `make test` command.\n    35Ôćĺ\n    36Ôćĺ```\n    37Ôćĺworkflow \"<name>\" {\n    38Ôćĺ  step implement {\n    39Ôćĺ    prompt = file(\"prompts/implement.md\")\n    40Ôćĺ    results = [success, fail]\n    41Ôćĺ  }\n    42Ôćĺ\n    43Ôćĺ  step test {\n    44Ôćĺ    run = \"make test 2>&1\"\n    45Ôćĺ    results = [success, fail]\n    46Ôćĺ  }\n    47Ôćĺ\n    48Ôćĺ  step fix {\n    49Ôćĺ    prompt = file(\"prompts/fix.md\")\n    50Ôćĺ    max_attempts = \"2\""}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AzU8HeMxKGnzFPbbezeUQh","session_id":"b83aa53c-b539-403e-957d-d27f065bd09c","uuid":"5d35b873-49ca-49fc-b2d1-01c5821e4058"}
