[2026-03-11T00:29:45Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017D7igncn66NfvThNNmycba","type":"tool_result","content":"     1Ôćĺ# Subdirectory Layout, Daemon-Side Extraction, and Poll Command\n     2Ôćĺ\n     3Ôćĺ**Date:** 2026-03-01\n     4Ôćĺ\n     5Ôćĺ## Overview\n     6Ôćĺ\n     7ÔćĺThree related changes to Cloche:\n     8Ôćĺ\n     9Ôćĺ1. Move cloche project files into a `./cloche/` subdirectory of the host project, separating host-level files (CLAUDE.md, .git, build config) from agent-level files.\n    10Ôćĺ2. Replace the in-container git push mechanism with daemon-side result extraction using `docker cp` and host-side git operations (with worktrees for concurrency).\n    11Ôćĺ3. Add a `poll` command that blocks until a run reaches a terminal state or its container has been dead for >1 minute.\n    12Ôćĺ\n    13Ôćĺ## 1. Directory Layout\n    14Ôćĺ\n    15Ôćĺ### Host project (user's repo root)\n    16Ôćĺ\n    17Ôćĺ```\n    18Ôćĺmy-project/\n    19ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ .git/\n    20ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ .gitignore\n    21ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ .gitworktrees/         # Daemon-managed git worktrees (gitignored)\n    22ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ CLAUDE.md              # Host-level agent instructions\n    23ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ README.md\n    24ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ cloche/                # Everything cloche manages\n    25ÔćĺÔöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ develop.cloche     # Workflow DSL file(s)\n    26ÔćĺÔöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ Dockerfile\n    27ÔćĺÔöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ CLAUDE.md          # Inner agent instructions\n    28ÔćĺÔöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ .cloche/\n    29ÔćĺÔöé   Ôöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ config\n    30ÔćĺÔöé   Ôöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ prompts/\n    31ÔćĺÔöé   Ôöé   Ôöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ implement.md\n    32ÔćĺÔöé   Ôöé   Ôöé   ÔööÔöÇÔöÇ fix.md\n    33ÔćĺÔöé   Ôöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ <run-id>/      # Per-run output (gitignored)\n    34ÔćĺÔöé   Ôöé   Ôöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ prompt.txt\n    35ÔćĺÔöé   Ôöé   Ôöé   ÔööÔöÇÔöÇ output/\n    36ÔćĺÔöé   Ôöé   ÔööÔöÇÔöÇ ...\n    37ÔćĺÔöé   ÔööÔöÇÔöÇ <source files>     # Project code the agent works on\n    38ÔćĺÔööÔöÇÔöÇ <host-level files>\n    39Ôćĺ```\n    40Ôćĺ\n    41Ôćĺ### Inside the container\n    42Ôćĺ\n    43Ôćĺ```\n    44Ôćĺ/workspace/                # = contents of host's ./cloche/\n    45ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ develop.cloche\n    46ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ Dockerfile\n    47ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ CLAUDE.md\n    48ÔćĺÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ .cloche/\n    49ÔćĺÔöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ config\n    50ÔćĺÔöé   ÔöťÔöÇÔöÇ prompts/"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AzU8HeMxKGnzFPbbezeUQh","session_id":"b83aa53c-b539-403e-957d-d27f065bd09c","uuid":"98bef03e-8dd6-4ddc-9aa3-cdf06d4f9fbf"}
