[2026-03-11T00:29:45Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013uiqMSo8tQQH16FB4t3cW8","type":"tool_result","content":"     1Ôćĺ# Project Pages Design\n     2Ôćĺ\n     3Ôćĺ**Date:** 2026-03-06\n     4Ôćĺ**Status:** Design\n     5Ôćĺ\n     6Ôćĺ## Problem\n     7Ôćĺ\n     8ÔćĺThe projects landing page shows only health dots and a \"View Runs\" link. There is no\n     9Ôćĺdedicated project page. Useful project-level information and controls are either missing\n    10Ôćĺor buried in other views.\n    11Ôćĺ\n    12Ôćĺ## Goal\n    13Ôćĺ\n    14ÔćĺAdd a dedicated `/projects/{name}` page with three panels:\n    15Ôćĺ\n    16Ôćĺ1. **Orchestrator control** ÔÇö view status, enable/disable the auto-poll loop, override concurrency\n    17Ôćĺ2. **Project info** ÔÇö Docker image, prompt file evolution history, project version\n    18Ôćĺ3. **Workflow view** ÔÇö read-only DAG of steps/wires, drillable to prompt/script content\n    19Ôćĺ\n    20Ôćĺ## Route\n    21Ôćĺ\n    22Ôćĺ```\n    23ÔćĺGET /projects/{name}\n    24Ôćĺ```\n    25Ôćĺ\n    26Ôćĺ`{name}` is the project label (same string used in `/api/projects/{name}/trigger`).\n    27ÔćĺThe handler resolves the label back to a project directory via `projectLabels()`.\n    28Ôćĺ\n    29ÔćĺProject cards on the landing page link to `/projects/{name}` instead of\n    30Ôćĺ`/runs?project=X`. The project page includes a compact recent-runs strip (last 10 dots)\n    31Ôćĺand a \"View all runs\" link to the filtered runs list.\n    32Ôćĺ\n    33Ôćĺ## Panel 1: Orchestrator Control\n    34Ôćĺ\n    35Ôćĺ### Display\n    36Ôćĺ- Status line: `Enabled / Disabled`, in-flight run count, concurrency limit\n    37Ôćĺ- Toggle button: **Enable** / **Disable** (controls the auto-poll loop for this project)\n    38Ôćĺ- Concurrency override: number input + **Apply** button (runtime only, resets on daemon restart)\n    39Ôćĺ\n    40Ôćĺ### API additions\n    41Ôćĺ\n    42Ôćĺ```\n    43ÔćĺGET  /api/projects/{name}/orchestrator\n    44ÔćĺPOST /api/projects/{name}/orchestrator/start\n    45ÔćĺPOST /api/projects/{name}/orchestrator/stop\n    46ÔćĺPOST /api/projects/{name}/orchestrator/concurrency   body: {\"concurrency\": N}\n    47Ôćĺ```\n    48Ôćĺ\n    49Ôćĺ`GET` response:\n    50Ôćĺ```json"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AzU8HeMxKGnzFPbbezeUQh","session_id":"b83aa53c-b539-403e-957d-d27f065bd09c","uuid":"c122b9e7-40dd-41bc-8556-dfb39cb56b62"}
