[2026-03-11T00:29:45Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AJkkNqYtjEvAyPufazTYc9","type":"tool_result","content":"     1Ôćĺ# Cloche Docker Base Image Design\n     2Ôćĺ\n     3Ôćĺ**Date:** 2026-03-06\n     4Ôćĺ**Status:** Design\n     5Ôćĺ\n     6Ôćĺ## Problem\n     7Ôćĺ\n     8ÔćĺThe default Dockerfile generated by `cloche init` builds `cloche-agent` from the cloche\n     9ÔćĺGo source inside the image. This only works for the cloche project itself (which has the\n    10Ôćĺsource available). For any other project, the template is broken out of the box.\n    11Ôćĺ\n    12ÔćĺThe root `Dockerfile` (used by the cloche project's own `.cloche/`) makes the same\n    13Ôćĺmistake, and is also unnecessarily large (based on `golang:1.25` for the final stage).\n    14Ôćĺ\n    15Ôćĺ## Solution\n    16Ôćĺ\n    17ÔćĺA `cloche-base` image: a minimal Debian-slim image with `git` and `cloche-agent`\n    18Ôćĺpre-installed. Projects start from this image and add their own tooling on top.\n    19Ôćĺ\n    20ÔćĺUsing `cloche-base` is **not required** ÔÇö projects may use any Dockerfile they like.\n    21Ôćĺ\n    22Ôćĺ---\n    23Ôćĺ\n    24Ôćĺ## `cloche-base` image contents\n    25Ôćĺ\n    26ÔćĺBuilt from `docker/cloche-base/Dockerfile` in the cloche repo.\n    27Ôćĺ\n    28Ôćĺ| Component | Why |\n    29Ôćĺ|-----------|-----|\n    30Ôćĺ| `debian:12-slim` | Small, stable, widely compatible |\n    31Ôćĺ| `git` | Required by `cloche-agent` for branch/commit operations |\n    32Ôćĺ| `ca-certificates` | TLS for any outbound requests agents make |\n    33Ôćĺ| `cloche-agent` binary | The in-container workflow executor |\n    34Ôćĺ| `agent` user | Unprivileged user; workdir `/workspace` owned by `agent` |\n    35Ôćĺ\n    36Ôćĺ**Not included:** Node.js, npm, claude-code, language runtimes, build tools. These are\n    37Ôćĺproject-specific and belong in the project's own Dockerfile.\n    38Ôćĺ\n    39Ôćĺ### `docker/cloche-base/Dockerfile`\n    40Ôćĺ\n    41Ôćĺ```dockerfile\n    42ÔćĺFROM golang:1.25 AS builder\n    43ÔćĺWORKDIR /src\n    44ÔćĺCOPY go.mod go.sum ./\n    45ÔćĺRUN go mod download\n    46ÔćĺCOPY . .\n    47ÔćĺRUN CGO_ENABLED=0 go build -o /cloche-agent ./cmd/cloche-agent\n    48Ôćĺ\n    49ÔćĺFROM debian:12-slim\n    50ÔćĺRUN apt-get update \\"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AzU8HeMxKGnzFPbbezeUQh","session_id":"b83aa53c-b539-403e-957d-d27f065bd09c","uuid":"c07c31b2-122d-4eb8-9740-16778e60be6a"}
