[2026-03-11T00:29:45Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TckP2u938tkFrVxRkwKxEN","type":"tool_result","content":"     1Ôćĺ# Project Settings File: config.toml\n     2Ôćĺ\n     3Ôćĺ**Date:** 2026-03-06\n     4Ôćĺ**Status:** Design\n     5Ôćĺ\n     6Ôćĺ## Problem\n     7Ôćĺ\n     8ÔćĺThe per-project settings file is `.cloche/config` with no extension, making it\n     9Ôćĺambiguous and inconsistent with the TOML library in use.\n    10Ôćĺ\n    11Ôćĺ## Change\n    12Ôćĺ\n    13ÔćĺRename to `.cloche/config.toml`. No backwards compatibility with the old filename.\n    14Ôćĺ\n    15Ôćĺ## Default file (created by `cloche init`)\n    16Ôćĺ\n    17Ôćĺ```toml\n    18Ôćĺ# Cloche project configuration\n    19Ôćĺ\n    20Ôćĺ[orchestration]\n    21Ôćĺenabled     = false\n    22Ôćĺconcurrency = 1\n    23Ôćĺworkflow    = \"develop\"\n    24Ôćĺ# tracker = \"beads\"\n    25Ôćĺ\n    26Ôćĺ[evolution]\n    27Ôćĺenabled           = true\n    28Ôćĺdebounce_seconds  = 30\n    29Ôćĺmin_confidence    = \"medium\"\n    30Ôćĺmax_prompt_bullets = 50\n    31Ôćĺ```\n    32Ôćĺ\n    33ÔćĺNotes:\n    34Ôćĺ- `orchestration.enabled` defaults to `false` so new projects don't start pulling tasks\n    35Ôćĺ  until explicitly opted in.\n    36Ôćĺ- All keys are present so the file is self-documenting.\n    37Ôćĺ- Commented-out keys (`tracker`) show optional overrides that rarely need changing.\n    38Ôćĺ\n    39Ôćĺ## Code changes\n    40Ôćĺ\n    41Ôćĺ| File | Change |\n    42Ôćĺ|------|--------|\n    43Ôćĺ| `internal/config/config.go` | `Load()`: change path from `\"config\"` to `\"config.toml\"` |\n    44Ôćĺ| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Add `config.toml` to the files created by init |\n    45Ôćĺ| `.cloche/config` (existing file in this repo) | Rename to `.cloche/config.toml` |\n    46Ôćĺ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b83aa53c-b539-403e-957d-d27f065bd09c","uuid":"75586a9d-873e-47d3-94d5-0ed00ad65d12","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-config-toml-design.md","content":"# Project Settings File: config.toml\n\n**Date:** 2026-03-06\n**Status:** Design\n\n## Problem\n\nThe per-project settings file is `.cloche/config` with no extension, making it\nambiguous and inconsistent with the TOML library in use.\n\n## Change\n\nRename to `.cloche/config.toml`. No backwards compatibility with the old filename.\n\n## Default file (created by `cloche init`)\n\n```toml\n# Cloche project configuration\n\n[orchestration]\nenabled     = false\nconcurrency = 1\nworkflow    = \"develop\"\n# tracker = \"beads\"\n\n[evolution]\nenabled           = true\ndebounce_seconds  = 30\nmin_confidence    = \"medium\"\nmax_prompt_bullets = 50\n```\n\nNotes:\n- `orchestration.enabled` defaults to `false` so new projects don't start pulling tasks\n  until explicitly opted in.\n- All keys are present so the file is self-documenting.\n- Commented-out keys (`tracker`) show optional overrides that rarely need changing.\n\n## Code changes\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `internal/config/config.go` | `Load()`: change path from `\"config\"` to `\"config.toml\"` |\n| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Add `config.toml` to the files created by init |\n| `.cloche/config` (existing file in this repo) | Rename to `.cloche/config.toml` |\n","numLines":46,"startLine":1,"totalLines":46}}}
