[2026-03-11T00:29:45Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015yJeRi7eRDzuk1Vteug3np","type":"tool_result","content":"     1Ôćĺ# Project Settings File: config.toml\n     2Ôćĺ\n     3Ôćĺ**Date:** 2026-03-06\n     4Ôćĺ**Status:** Design\n     5Ôćĺ\n     6Ôćĺ## Problem\n     7Ôćĺ\n     8ÔćĺThe per-project settings file is `.cloche/config` with no extension, making it\n     9Ôćĺambiguous and inconsistent with the TOML library in use.\n    10Ôćĺ\n    11Ôćĺ## Change\n    12Ôćĺ\n    13ÔćĺRename to `.cloche/config.toml`. No backwards compatibility with the old filename.\n    14Ôćĺ\n    15Ôćĺ## Default file (created by `cloche init`)\n    16Ôćĺ\n    17Ôćĺ```toml\n    18Ôćĺ# Cloche project configuration\n    19Ôćĺ\n    20Ôćĺ[orchestration]\n    21Ôćĺconcurrency        = 1\n    22Ôćĺstagger_seconds    = 1.0\n    23Ôćĺ# list_tasks_command = \"bash .cloche/scripts/ready-tasks.sh\"\n    24Ôćĺ# dedup_seconds    = 300\n    25Ôćĺ\n    26Ôćĺ[evolution]\n    27Ôćĺenabled           = true\n    28Ôćĺdebounce_seconds  = 30\n    29Ôćĺmin_confidence    = \"medium\"\n    30Ôćĺmax_prompt_bullets = 50\n    31Ôćĺ```\n    32Ôćĺ\n    33ÔćĺNotes:\n    34Ôćĺ- `orchestration.concurrency` defaults to `1` (single run at a time).\n    35Ôćĺ- `orchestration.stagger_seconds` adds delay between consecutive launches (default `1.0`).\n    36Ôćĺ- `orchestration.list_tasks_command` (optional) is a shell command that outputs a JSON array of\n    37Ôćĺ  task objects (`[{\"id\":\"...\",\"title\":\"...\",\"description\":\"...\"}]`). When set, the daemon\n    38Ôćĺ  picks tasks and passes the ID via `CLOCHE_TASK_ID` env var.\n    39Ôćĺ- `orchestration.dedup_seconds` (default `300`) prevents reassignment of the same task ID\n    40Ôćĺ  within the timeout window.\n    41Ôćĺ- Commented-out keys show optional overrides that rarely need changing.\n    42Ôćĺ\n    43Ôćĺ## Code changes\n    44Ôćĺ\n    45Ôćĺ| File | Change |\n    46Ôćĺ|------|--------|\n    47Ôćĺ| `internal/config/config.go` | `Load()`: change path from `\"config\"` to `\"config.toml\"` |\n    48Ôćĺ| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Add `config.toml` to the files created by init |\n    49Ôćĺ| `.cloche/config` (existing file in this repo) | Rename to `.cloche/config.toml` |\n    50Ôćĺ"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b83aa53c-b539-403e-957d-d27f065bd09c","uuid":"2005c5e4-5d68-48b0-8f3a-1db9c5315cbc","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-06-config-toml-design.md","content":"# Project Settings File: config.toml\n\n**Date:** 2026-03-06\n**Status:** Design\n\n## Problem\n\nThe per-project settings file is `.cloche/config` with no extension, making it\nambiguous and inconsistent with the TOML library in use.\n\n## Change\n\nRename to `.cloche/config.toml`. No backwards compatibility with the old filename.\n\n## Default file (created by `cloche init`)\n\n```toml\n# Cloche project configuration\n\n[orchestration]\nconcurrency        = 1\nstagger_seconds    = 1.0\n# list_tasks_command = \"bash .cloche/scripts/ready-tasks.sh\"\n# dedup_seconds    = 300\n\n[evolution]\nenabled           = true\ndebounce_seconds  = 30\nmin_confidence    = \"medium\"\nmax_prompt_bullets = 50\n```\n\nNotes:\n- `orchestration.concurrency` defaults to `1` (single run at a time).\n- `orchestration.stagger_seconds` adds delay between consecutive launches (default `1.0`).\n- `orchestration.list_tasks_command` (optional) is a shell command that outputs a JSON array of\n  task objects (`[{\"id\":\"...\",\"title\":\"...\",\"description\":\"...\"}]`). When set, the daemon\n  picks tasks and passes the ID via `CLOCHE_TASK_ID` env var.\n- `orchestration.dedup_seconds` (default `300`) prevents reassignment of the same task ID\n  within the timeout window.\n- Commented-out keys show optional overrides that rarely need changing.\n\n## Code changes\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `internal/config/config.go` | `Load()`: change path from `\"config\"` to `\"config.toml\"` |\n| `cmd/cloche/init.go` | Add `config.toml` to the files created by init |\n| `.cloche/config` (existing file in this repo) | Rename to `.cloche/config.toml` |\n","numLines":50,"startLine":1,"totalLines":50}}}
